name: Wattson Apex Legends
description:
This is my first ever LoRA. Hope you enjoy it!

If you want to support me, check out my Patreon for exclusive content and commissions: https://www.patreon.com/Eminic

LoRA model for the character Wattson from Apex Legends. Trained for 20 epochs on the Hassaku checkpoint model.

LoRA weight can be anywhere from 0.1-1. It should work fine at 1.

CFG scale 6-8, although you can try experimenting.

Trigger word (optional): "Wattson"

This LoRA is very NSFW friendly, but it can do SFW images just fine as well.

Sometimes multiple subjects/fractals may appear but it is rare for this to happen, and will get ironed out over the next couple updates.

How to use LoRA's in automatic1111's web-ui:

  • Update webui (use git pullor redownload it)

  • Copy the file to stable-diffusion-webui/models/lora

  • Select your LoRA like in this video

  • Make sure to select your desired weight, or leave it at the default of 1. (example: <lora:WattsonLora:1> is 1 weight, <lora:WattsonLora:0.5> is 0.5 weight)

If you like this LoRA, I would appreciate a heart as thanks :)
